  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was a little bit eerie, because you never had much warning about when those were gonna come.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the invasion was well underway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were just playing catch-up at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only by radio, and there was no official communications to tell you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There again, you're in a rather narrow segment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You knew what your unit was doing, but not necessarily what everybody north, south, or east and west was doing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sorry?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we went to several different staging areas, and it looked like we were still trying to catch up with the troops to see what assignment we might draw.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Finally, we ended up in a camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we took a camp in Frankfurt am Main after we'd crossed the Rhine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we stayed there for a few days in a race track.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we spent some time looking for souvenirs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At one time they must have had a-- Olympic activities there, because we just found some old Olympic flags there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we found some medical equipment that had been abandoned by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we took some of that in and took what we could use to supplement our table of organization-- and equipment, I should say.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in Germany at that point.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, one night we had just recently been assigned to Patton's Third Army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the middle of the night we were called out and said we're going to move out, destination unknown.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went some 120, 130 miles, I think, in one night, which was a long ways for a military unit to go in one day-- and got near enough to the front that it really frightened us.",
      "word_count": 38
    }
  ],
